<lb n="0400b06" ed="T"/>娑<note place="inline">引</note>　度吽<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">二</note></p>
<lb n="0400b07" ed="T"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgT18p0400b0701" style="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「以金剛步而漸進，<caesura/>南布第二曼拏羅，</l>
<lb n="0400b08" ed="T"/><l>彼中應畫本部尊，<caesura/>頂冠中有如來像，</l>
